		<p class="firstparagraph"><strong>Puzzle 1.</strong> A helium balloon is attached to the bottom of a truck. If the truck driver accelerates the truck in the direction of travel, in which direction relative to the driver does the balloon move? <a href="writing/2017-03-10-puzzle-1.html" class="link">solution</a></p>
